org.jasig.cas.support.geo.maxmind

Class MaxmindDatabaseGeoLocationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.support.geo.maxmind.MaxmindDatabaseGeoLocationService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeoLocationService

    @Service(value="maxmindDatabaseGeoLocationService")
public class MaxmindDatabaseGeoLocationService
extends java.lang.Object
implements GeoLocationService
    This is MaxmindDatabaseGeoLocationService that reads geo data from a maxmind database and constructs a geo location based on the ip address. Default caching of the databases is enabled by default.
    Since:
    4.3.0
